reviewText: Has never been a team like this, never more real portrayal and never more interesting story lines.

Disc 5 is a waste of time.  It plays half an episode and then freezes and skips to the last half of the next episode.  Tried everything to make it work, but it remains useless.  Haven't got to disc 6 yet, but trying to follow the story line of the series makes this impossible.

IT PLAYED WELL EXCEPT FOR ONE EPISODE.
THE DVD SKIPPED AND STOPPED PLAYING.
I have been enjoying this series becouse the acting is so good. The picture is clear and the sound is good. It is hard to skip the intro and credits though.
